node.text: Curious to hear what the secrets behind dermatology are? Dermatologist @lucasponti & actress @florbertottiok  from Argentina deep dive into it and give us their precious tips! Thanks to everyone who joined the live 💙 #larocheposay

How to protect your skin this summer ?☀️
#Skinismorethanskin – Dermatologist @dra.abrilsandoval & @Josephinewit – We are joined by Dr. Abril Sandoval C. and Dr Josephine Wit to discuss photo protection and how to find the right routine for your skin. 
Thanks to everyone who joined in live and shared questions! 💙

All languages spoken here! Feel free to talk to us at anytime.

#larocheposay #sunprotection #lifechangingdermatology 

Global official page from La Roche-Posay, France.

node.title: My skincare secret: daily sun protection

node.text:
During this week’s live, @drzainab.dermatology and Professor Niki Ralph from @instituteofdermatologists discussed the impact that skin conditions can have on our quality of life. 

Thanks to everyone who joined the live, and feel free to ask us your questions. You’re not alone 💙

node.title: How do skin conditions impact quality of life?

We all know how texture is important when choosing a sunscreen.

With Anthelios Invisible Fluid SPF 50+ and its non-greasy, non-sticky and ultra-fluid texture, protect your skin against UV rays! 

Add this product to your daily routine and see the results for yourself: an invisible finish and ultra-high protection. Your skin will thank you!

node.text:
Hey there, we hope you’re having a great day! Have you already applied suncare today ? If not, here’s a quick gentle reminder to apply sun protection whenever you go outside ! And if you are under constant sun exposure, don’t forget to reapply every 2 hours ! For high protection against UVA and UVB, use Anthelios Invisible Fluid SPF50+. Your skin will thank you. ☀️

All languages spoken here ! Feel free to talk to us at anytime.
#larocheposay #sunprotection

node.text:
Thank you very much, @vanjnj, for sharing your skin story with us. 💙 As you said, very dry skin can affect your daily life whether you are a child, teenager or adult. That’s why it is essential that you choose the dermatological product that suits your skin. For example, Cicaplast Baume B5 helps repair and strengthen the skin barrier, soothes and relieves your skin from redness and burning sensations. Are you prone to these concerns ? Feel free to share your story with us by commenting on this post.� 

All languages spoken here ! Feel free to talk to us at anytime.
#larocheposay #cicaplast #sensitiveskin #lrplove

node.text:
We were delighted to hear from @carlos.skincare on how he’s enjoying the benefits of Effaclar mat right now. Thank you for this great portrait! 

“MATnificient! This moisturizing-mattifying cream from La Roche-Posay is “Effaclar Mat”. It’s an ideal cream for oily or acne-prone skin who want to control their shine and regulate oil, I really love its light gel texture, great for in the morning since it’s when my skin is at its oiliest. 
Honestly it works almost instantaneously, you really notice how you no longer have that shine on your face and feels soft and smooth.” 

And you, is this product part of your routine? Feel free to give us your feedback by commenting this post! 💙

All languages spoken here! Feel free to talk to us at anytime.
#larocheposay #skincare #effaclar #lrplove #lifechangingdermatology
